com.hp.jipp.encoding

Interface Attribute<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PrettyPrintable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseAttribute, EmptyAttribute, UnknownAttribute

    public Attribute<T>
extends PrettyPrintable

    An IPP attribute, which is a named list of 0 or more values. Values are parsed into the most natural Java type that can encode the supplied data.
